    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Chess\" title=\"Chess\">Chess</a> * <a href=\"/Chess_Position\" title=\"Chess Position\">Position</a> * Initial Position</b> \n</p><p><b>Initial Position</b>, (Initial Setup, Array) \nthe position where the <a href=\"/Chess_Game\" title=\"Chess Game\">game of chess</a> starts. <a href=\"/Pieces\" title=\"Pieces\">Pieces</a> and <a href=\"/King\" title=\"King\">king</a> <a href=\"/Occupancy\" title=\"Occupancy\">occupy</a> their first rank, the <a href=\"/Pawn\" title=\"Pawn\">pawns</a> their second. White and black men are mirrored vertically. In orthodox classical chess, the kings occupy the e-file, the <a href=\"/Queen\" title=\"Queen\">queen</a> the d-file. <a href=\"/Bishop\" title=\"Bishop\">bishop</a> files are c and f, <a href=\"/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> has b and g, and <a href=\"/Rook\" title=\"Rook\">rooks</a> a and h files respectively. In <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Fischer Random Chess</a> or Chess960, there are <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chess960_starting_position\">960 starting positions</a> randomly determined and set up.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#FEN\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">FEN</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Diagram\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Diagram</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Ambiguity\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ambiguity</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Perft\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Perft</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"FEN\"><a href=\"/Forsyth-Edwards_Notation\" title=\"Forsyth-Edwards Notation\">FEN</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: FEN\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<pre>rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Diagram\">Diagram</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Diagram\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<table class=\"fentt\" style=\"font-size:24pt\"><tr><td>&#160;</td><td class=\"cols\">abcdefgh</td><td>&#160;</td></tr><tr><td class=\"rows\">8<br/>7<br/>6<br/>5<br/>4<br/>3<br/>2<br/>1<br/></td><td class=\"board\" style=\"width: 8em;\"><div class=\"board\"><div class=\"sq\">    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/></div><div class=\"pcbg\"><br/><br/>        <br/>        <br/>        <br/>        <br/><br/><br/></div><div class=\"pcfg\">♜♞♝♛♚♝♞♜<br/>♟♟♟♟♟♟♟♟<br/>        <br/>        <br/>        <br/>        <br/>♙♙♙♙♙♙♙♙<br/>♖♘♗♕♔♗♘♖<br/></div></div></td><td class=\"rows\">8<br/>7<br/>6<br/>5<br/>4<br/>3<br/>2<br/>1<br/></td></tr><tr><td>&#160;</td><td class=\"cols\">abcdefgh</td><td>&#160;</td></tr></table>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ambiguity\">Ambiguity</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Ambiguity\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In the context of <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a>, the initial position might also refer the <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">root</a> of the <a href=\"/Search_Tree\" title=\"Search Tree\">search tree</a>, which is not necessarily the initial position of the game of chess.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Perft\">Perft</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Perft\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Movepath enumerations (<a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">perft</a>) generated by <a href=\"/Symbolic\" title=\"Symbolic\">Symbolic</a> for the <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Initial Position</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Perft(10)_20_draft_9_Positions\" title=\"Perft(10) 20 draft 9 Positions\">Perft(10) 20 draft 9 Positions</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(10)_400_draft_8_Positions\" title=\"Perft(10) 400 draft 8 Positions\">Perft(10) 400 draft 8 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(11)_20_draft_10_Positions\" title=\"Perft(11) 20 draft 10 Positions\">Perft(11) 20 draft 10 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(11)_400_draft_9_Positions\" title=\"Perft(11) 400 draft 9 Positions\">Perft(11) 400 draft 9 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(12)_20_draft_11_Positions\" title=\"Perft(12) 20 draft 11 Positions\">Perft(12) 20 draft 11 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(12)_400_draft_10_Positions\" title=\"Perft(12) 400 draft 10 Positions\">Perft(12) 400 draft 10 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(13)_20_draft_12_Positions\" title=\"Perft(13) 20 draft 12 Positions\">Perft(13) 20 draft 12 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft(13)_400_draft_11_Positions\" title=\"Perft(13) 400 draft 11 Positions\">Perft(13) 400 draft 11 Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Initial_Position_Summary\" title=\"Initial Position Summary\">Initial Position Summary</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboard_Board-Definition\" title=\"Bitboard Board-Definition\">Bitboard Board-Definition</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_List\" title=\"Move List\">Move List</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Opening\" title=\"Opening\">Opening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft_Results\" title=\"Perft Results\">Perft Results</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">Root</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Test-Positions</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66335\">Komodo 11.2.2 - Initial position until depth 54</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller\" title=\"Andreas Strangmüller\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 15, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66340\">Stockfish 8 - Initial position until depth 59</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller\" title=\"Andreas Strangmüller\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66347\">Cfish-54302a... Search of startpos to depth 50</a> by <a href=\"/Louis_Zulli\" title=\"Louis Zulli\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 17, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/CFish\" title=\"CFish\">CFish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66935\">Stockfish 180113 - Initial position until depth 65</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller\" title=\"Andreas Strangmüller\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=67097\">Houdini 6 - Initial position until depth 50</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller\" title=\"Andreas Strangmüller\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 13, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Initial_Position&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external